{"tid":1563152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「急」超需要關於新屋嶺既文宣！","createTime":"2019-09-12T09:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T14:11:21.000Z","uid":215894,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3b30288da0cdbb9cf37de7973048aa6e8df59162","tid":1563152,"uid":215894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"最近小弟都有勤補自己個區既連儂牆，但我發現無論係連登同連儂牆，關於新屋嶺既話題係極之有少！上網都只係搵到好少！<br />\n最近被自殺既新聞愈黎愈多，班差佬完全當我地唔用腦諗野，絕大多數自殺既案件上都有極大既疑點，例如跳樓完全無巨響，而且自殺時間點極之吻合，好明顯班黑警係新屋嶺向我地手足施行酷刑，紙包不住火，為左毀滅證據佢地將我地既手足變成被自殺既目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好希望係炒車，但一日未搞清楚件事只會無限地將事件合理化<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以除左宣傳9.15遊行同各區既人鏈之外，務必煲大新屋嶺同最近被自殺既黑警罪行<br />\n強烈請求文宣組製作相關既文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家似乎對被自殺既問題無咁高關注度，但大家要清楚既係呢d被自殺既人係我地手足呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58291553385211daafccb608f97ff5338815515","tid":1563152,"uid":215894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:57:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e17c62086077d7864e9bb95beec80767609cebb5","tid":1563152,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:57:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d717c53bd92a74fbcdb9c8f32525edcf5ebf69b5","tid":1563152,"uid":129537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebaac6b5c82e69c5c944dbb203510755e744c3de","tid":1563152,"uid":215894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:58:33.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"45b1f4e8f65dfbdc5787e736da84db1258e856cb","tid":1563152,"uid":215894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:00:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390bf78d921e32295447af379df4e0f54168f2c2","tid":1563152,"uid":215894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:00:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd691061b45db02158ac9c0fa5a2154d188a178d","tid":1563152,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:01:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"120e828819bb8e32c4bb305fba59e6a69a909782","tid":1563152,"uid":215894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:01:48.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"87a14a651361a9d4b4cd858a95ea7099698a138d","tid":1563152,"uid":277084,"li